<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>TKAPI 视频数据分析工具</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="/css/app.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="site-page">
  <header class="site-header">
    <a class="site-logo" href="/">TKAPI</a>
    <nav class="site-nav" aria-label="TKAPI navigation">
      <a href="/features">功能介绍</a>
      <a href="/keywords">关键词搜索</a>
      <a href="/settings/tiktok">TikTok API</a>
      <a href="/terms">Terms</a>
      <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="site-hero">
      <div class="site-hero-content">
        <p class="site-kicker">Keyword-based social video analytics dashboard</p>
        <h1>TKAPI 视频数据分析工具</h1>
        <p class="site-summary">
          通过关键词追踪 TikTok、YouTube、Instagram、Facebook、X 等平台的视频数据，分析播放量、点赞、评论、收藏、分享和趋势变化。
        </p>
        <div class="site-actions">
          <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="/keywords">开始关键词分析</a>
          <a class="btn btn-success btn-lg" href="/settings/tiktok">连接 TikTok API</a>
          <a class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg" href="/features">查看功能介绍</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="site-section" aria-label="TKAPI capabilities">
      <div class="feature-grid">
        <a class="feature-card feature-link" href="/keywords">
          <h2>关键词搜索</h2>
          <p>输入关键词，获取相关视频数据。</p>
        </a>
        <a class="feature-card feature-link" href="/keywords">
          <h2>视频数据排行榜</h2>
          <p>按播放量、点赞数、评论数、收藏数、分享数排序。</p>
        </a>
        <a class="feature-card feature-link" href="/keywords">
          <h2>平台分类</h2>
          <p>支持 TikTok、YouTube、Instagram、Facebook、X 等平台分开查看。</p>
        </a>
        <a class="feature-card feature-link" href="/features">
          <h2>趋势分析</h2>
          <p>分析关键词下视频数据的增长速度和热度变化。</p>
        </a>
        <a class="feature-card feature-link" href="/settings/tiktok">
          <h2>TikTok API 授权</h2>
          <p>通过 TikTok 官方 API 授权获取允许范围内的数据。</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
